  "detailed_description": "Maria is a free girl, definitely of legal drinking age in any country.<br>She heads to a masquerade party dressed as a bunny.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Vitaly, by a stroke of luck, happens to be at the same club, sets his eyes on her, and offers to buy her a tasty drink.<br>For unknown reasons, Maria loses consciousness, and Vitaly, being a true gentleman, places her limp body in the trunk and takes her to his country residence to let her have a good sleep.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Upon waking up, Maria realizes that Vitaly brought her to his place. But she’s not that kind of girl. So she firmly decides that she needs to escape at any cost...<br><strong>But for free!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What we gonna do?</h2>You need to sneak away from Vitaly’s country residence in a luxurious silver Haval.<br>Unlock doors, break planks, open electrical panels, smash floors, throw dishes, distract Vitaly with loud noises, and enjoy PS4-era graphics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features of the Game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomized placement of items needed to escape this evil residence!<br></li><li>A mysterious admirer chasing you no matter where you hide.<br></li><li>A seductive heroine who leaves no one indifferent.<br></li><li>Multiple escape routes planned. Eventually.<br></li><li>Easter eggs galore!<br></li><li>Real reflections in mirrors! When was the last time you saw that?<br></li><li>You can hide in the toilet.<br></li><li>Become successful and rich!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><i>Success and wealth not included in the game.</i></u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
